long as the rapid\naccretion is maintained in the later stage, protostars will become SMSs, which\neventually produce seeds for the high-z SMBHs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2013 11:53:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
